Package: MRBEE.TRAN
Type: Package
Title: Tran-Ancestry Mendelian Randomization using Bias-Corrected Estimating Equation and Transfer Learning
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yihe Yang
Maintainer: Yihe Yang <yxy1234@case.edu>
Description: This package performs tran-ancestry multivariate Mendelian randomization. The central idea is using transfer learning to gain power from Eourpean population. It is characterized by the removal of measurement error bias caused by the estimation error of GWAS effect size estimates using an unbiased estimating function in measurement error analysis. It also utilizes a pleiotropy test to dynamically detect and remove potential pleiotropy, making the causal effect robust to pleiotropy.
